---
title: Backyard BBQ-Style Chicken Dinner with Sugar Snap Peas and Potato Salad
description: If you're craving some BBQ but you just don't feel like firing up the grill, we've got you covered! This dish delivers all the joys of that backyard BBQ sesh, but it all happens in the kitchen in under 30 minutes!
